title: 24 - Emmy Blotnick

description: You’ve won an Emmy! An Emmy Blotnick, that is. In your ears. On this episode. You may know her from Colbert, Conan, and Comedy Central, but now you’ll get to know her even better through her tale of travel and misfortune. Here are five words to describe this episode: keep track of your keys.
